---
title: Chicken Breasts Noodle Bake with Cheddar-Breadcrumb Topper
description: This dish transforms all the wholesome comfort of chicken noodle soup into a bake! Buttered breadcrumbs and cheddar cheese get golden when baked on top of the creamy chicken and noodle mix. Use an oven-proof pan to save yourself from doing extra dishes!
